切换到 thcl 数据库，如果不存在则自动创建：

[source, bash]
> use thcl

[source, text]
----
> db.createUser(
  {
    user: "thcl",
    pwd: "thcl",
    roles: [ { role: "readWrite", db: "thcl" } ]
  }
)
----

